  <brief_title>Non-invasive Methods and Surgical Risk Stratification in Cirrhotics Undergoing Elective Extrahepatic Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>&quot;Prognostic Role of Portal Hypertension Assessed by Non-invasive Methods to Stratify Surgical Risk in Compensated Advanced Chronic Liver Disease Patients Undergoing Elective Extrahepatic Surgery: ELASTOSURGERY STUDY.&quot;</official_title>
